name: The Pumpkin Queen
description:
I was walking through the woods, and I saw her, The elusive Pumpkin Queen! I was able to snap this pic and narrowly escape her clasp. I did it all for the sake of science. And now we have proof of her existence.

See her in motion at https://youtu.be/diSzxRaHWAY

model: Sawyer Croft
body paint and photography by Roustan (bodypainter.com)
